    <item>
      <title>数据公布后，国债涨跌互现，两年期国债在拍卖中持有收益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/treasuries-steady-before-debt-auction-rush-and-inflation-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一份报告显示美国消费者信心上升以及市场为周二的两次票据拍卖做准备之后，国债涨跌互现，短期国债收益率小幅走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/treasuries-steady-before-debt-auction-rush-and-inflation-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 10:44:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新兴货币削减涨幅，股市因美联储鹰派言论而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/emerging-markets-edge-down-before-elections-take-center-stage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美联储官员的鹰派言论和强于预期的美国消费者信心抑制了风险偏好，新兴市场货币收窄涨幅，股市扩大跌幅。投资者还期待南非、墨西哥和印度的选举结果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/emerging-markets-edge-down-before-elections-take-center-stage</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 09:31:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
